msg: WSCOMMONS-254: DocumentImpl#getOMDocumentElement() made the incorrect assumption that only an element can be the first child of a Document. This is incorrect. There can be DTDs, comments and processing instructions before the document element. Replaced the if statement by a while loop to fix this.
